Package: rapsim
Type: Package
Title: R for APSIM Classic
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bangyou", "Zheng", 
               email = "bangyou.zheng@csiro.au", 
               role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The Agricultural Production Systems sIMulator ('APSIM') is a widely
    used to simulate the agricultural systems for multiple crops. This package 
    is designed to create, modify and run 'apsim' files in the 'APSIM' 
    Classic <https://www.apsim.info/>.
